      "purposeInStoryline": "This is the PREDICT opening lesson. It launches the anchoring phenomenon, surfaces prior knowledge and misconceptions, and opens the Driving Question Board (DQB) so that every subsequent lesson can be framed as answering a question the class itself has posed.",
